### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

### Get Random Country Clues
GET http://localhost:3000/api/country

###

### Submit Guess - Example Guess
POST http://localhost:3000/api/guess
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "guess": "Italy"
}

###

### Submit Guess - Wrong Guess
POST http://localhost:3000/api/guess
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "guess": "WrongCountry"
}

###

### Submit Guess - Empty JSON Body
POST http://localhost:3000/api/guess
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### Submit Guess - Missing guess Field
POST http://localhost:3000/api/guess
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "somethingElse": "value"
}

###

### Submit Guess - Non-String Guess
POST http://localhost:3000/api/guess
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "guess": 42
}
